---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import DisclaimerBanner from '../components/DisclaimerBanner.astro';

const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Cancellation Policy', href: '/cancellation-policy' }
];
---
<Layout title="Cancellation and Refund Policy">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Cancellation and Refund Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700">
      <p>We respect your time and ours. Please review our policies regarding scheduling, cancellations, and refunds.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Consultation Cancellations</h2>
      <p>If you need to cancel or reschedule, we require at least <strong>24 hours notice</strong>. Cancellations made within 24 hours of the scheduled session may be subject to a cancellation fee or forfeiture of the session fee.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Refunds</h2>
      <p>Refunds for services are generally provided if requested before the 24-hour cancellation window. Digital resources and digital courses are non-refundable once downloaded or accessed, unless explicitly stated otherwise.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8">Provider Responsibility</h2>
      <p>Each independent provider operating through our directory manages their own schedule and billing. Specific cancellation terms may vary by provider. Always confirm these details directly with your chosen specialist before booking.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
